1. *Lusi* se po parku. (He/She is strolling around the park.)
2. Ona je *lusila* po ulici. (She was walking down the street.)
3. On je *lusio* po šumi. (He was wandering in the forest.)
4. Ona će *lusiti* po tržnici. (She will be walking around the market.)
5. *Lusio* je po gradu. (He was wandering around the city.)